speaker: Agent
text: Hello, this is Mark calling from XYZ Collections. Am I speaking with Sarah?

speaker: Customer
text: No, this is not Sarah. You have the wrong number.

speaker: Agent
text: I apologize for the mix-up. I'm calling about an outstanding balance on an account.

speaker: Customer
text: I really don't think I know anything about that.

speaker: Agent
text: Could you confirm your name to ensure I'm not reaching the right person?

speaker: Customer
text: Sure, my name is Emily, and I don’t have any accounts with your company.

speaker: Agent
text: Thank you, Emily. I’ll make sure to update our records.

speaker: Customer
text: I appreciate that. Have a good day.
